OL,6,FA former firefighter racially abused
OL,7,Fstaff and urinated on the floor of a
OL,8,FChinese takeaway, a jury has ruled
OL,9,Ffollowing a trial.
OL,11,FGareth Hancock, a former South Wales
OL,12,FFire and Rescue Service employee, was
OL,13,Fconvicted of one count of racially
OL,14,Faggravated intentional harassment,
OL,15,Falarm or distress, and one count of
OL,16,Fcriminal damage, following a three-day
OL,17,Ftrial at Cardiff Crown Court.
