OL,3,CFirefighter racially abused staff and
OL,4,Curinated on floor of Chinese takeaway
OL,6,FHancock, who had been stationed at
OL,7,FEbbw Vale at the time of the incident
OL,8,Fin June 2023, attended the family-run
OL,9,FYummies Chinese takeaway in Tredegar,
OL,10,FBlaenau Gwent, along with fellow off-
OL,11,Fduty firefighters after consuming
OL,12,Fbetween six and eight pints of lager.
OL,14,FThe 35-year-old, from Brynmawr, had
OL,15,Fdenied the charges.
OL,17,FHancock is due to be sentenced at
OL,18,FNewport Crown Court on November 14.
